  "text": "As described in our previous publications, [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] the Ab peptides were labeled with 125 I using the chloramine-T reaction, and the product was dialyzed to remove unconjugated 125 I. The purity of the 125 I-labeled protein was determined by trichloroacetic acid (TCA) assay.",
